Start HTTP server (REST API)

Usage: normalize serve http [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -p, --port <PORT>  Port to listen on [default: 8080]
      --openapi      Output OpenAPI spec and exit (don't start server)
  -r, --root <ROOT>  Root directory (defaults to current directory)
      --json         Output as JSON
      --jq <EXPR>    Filter JSON output with jq expression (implies --json)
      --pretty       Human-friendly output with colors and formatting
      --compact      Compact output without colors (overrides TTY detection)
  -h, --help         Print help
